com.microsoft.azure.management.sql

Interface RecommendedElasticPoolOperations

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    RecommendedElasticPoolOperationsImpl

    public interface RecommendedElasticPoolOperations
    Represents all the operations for operating on Azure SQL Recommended Elastic Pools. Contains operations to: Retrieve.

                                      String serverName,
                                      String recommendedElasticPoolName)
                               throws IOException,
                                      ServiceException
        Returns information about an Azure SQL Recommended Elastic Pool.
        Parameters:
        resourceGroupName - Required. The name of the Resource Group to which the Azure SQL Recommended Server belongs.
        serverName - Required. The name of the Azure SQL Database Server for which the Azure SQL Recommended Elastic Pool is.
        recommendedElasticPoolName - Required. The name of the Azure SQL Recommended Elastic Pool to be retrieved.
        Returns:
